  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Periocular blockade with 12.5 mm needle is as effective as block with 25 mm needle for
      patients undergoing Pars Plana Vitrectomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The author wants to see the effect of short needle in patients undergoing retinal surgery.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
